      <h2>Do I Need a Fishing License in Alabama?</h2>
      <p>Yes. Any person age 16 or older fishing in Alabama public waters must have a valid Alabama freshwater fishing license. This applies to residents and non-residents alike. Children under 16 are exempt from the license requirement.</p>

